  • public abstract class DialogCancelDeleteDoneFragment
extends DialogCancelActionDoneFragment
    Standard 3-button Dialog for "Cancel" (left button), "Delete" (middle button), "Done" (right button). By default will show a delete confirmation dialog DialogDeleteConfirmFragment if "Delete" is pressed and hasDataToDelete() returns true.
